data.description: You will not want to miss this Brick house on the South hill. Inside has beautiful hardwood floors, multiple new windows, a year old furnace, and washer dryer hookups in the basement and the kitchen. Downstairs in mostly unfinished with one non conforming bedroom, with so many possibilities, with the bathroom in the basement already there. Outside has a fenced in back yard, drive through garage with ally access, ally trash service, and oversided garage. This street is one of the first to get plowed in the winter. FHA approved, last year the house got refinanced on an FHA loan.   Seller is offering a $1000 credit for landscaping at closing.
